@startuml vertical-lifecycle
title Vertical (Interest Domain) Lifecycle

[*] --> Draft : Domain proposed by Region/Country

Draft --> Requested : Submitted for Umbrella Approval
Requested --> Reviewed : Compliance & Capability Review

state Reviewed {
  [*] --> Approved
}

Approved --> Active : Credentials & Budgets Allocated
Active --> Restricted : Audit in Progress
Active --> Suspended : Governance Hold

Active --> Deprecated : Mission Complete
Deprecated --> Archived : Data Frozen

@enduml
